  <div class="left" style="float:right">
    <div class="box">
      <div class="title">Offering Summary</div>
      <div class="body" style="margin:10px !important;">
        <ul class="redArrows">

          <li>Stable, tax-efficient monthly principal repayments of 5% per annum throughout the term of the Notes
</li><li> Leveraged exposure through a notional loan facility provided at 1-Month BA Rate, plus 25 bps per annum
</li><li> Loan on additional leveraged exposure is non-recourse to investors
</li><li> Annual fees of 1.80 % charged against the Net Value of the Note Portfolio (i.e. excluding leveraged exposure)
</li><li> Notes are tradable at their Net Asset Value in a daily secondary market provided by BMO Capital Markets (subject to availability as outlined in the Prospectus). An early trading charge will be applicable for the first three years only.</li>

        </ul>

      </div>
